      "comment": "POCKET TALK (4) was well fancied last time on the strength of his recent form but could only manage second (19.05) at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from six starts. Can measure up this time. INFAMOUS STATHAM (8) has a strong record this trip with nine wins and three placings from 20 starts. Missed the frame latest (18.50) when fifth over 320m at Richmond in a NG. Suited here and expected to run well. SPEEDY PIE (3) won again and recorded an impressive time after running them ragged making it three straight, scoring at this track over 400m (22.23). Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another bold showing. MISS GLAMOURPUSS (2) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
